  {
    "title": "Meta Heroes",
    "depth": 0,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "It is recommended that you practice each EXP lane hero at least once, so that you know enemy skill types, cooldowns, and learn matchups and recommended skill builds for different heroes."
          },
          {
            "text": "An EXP laner will determine the initial direction of a match."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "These heroes are currently meta and will dominate the lane (most of the time as shown in tournaments) if you mastered them:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "These heroes are good for solo queue and easy to master:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "If you are going EXP lane, it is better to buy the Dagger than the Boots for higher physical damage in the early game as your abilities will mostly use Physical Attack to calculate damage.",
